  "description": "Requests are rate limited per API key to 120 requests per 1-minute window. When you exceed the limit the API responds with HTTP 429 Too Many Requests, including a 'Retry-After' header (integer number of seconds to wait before retrying) plus 'RateLimit-Limit', 'RateLimit-Remaining' and 'RateLimit-Reset' (seconds until the window resets). Respect 'Retry-After' before sending further requests.",
